data.description:
Located in the heart of thriving Biddeford overlooking the Saco River with some limited views. The 1st floor apartment of this 3 unit has been home & owner occupied since 1961. This building has been respectfully cared for and maintained and offers a 4 car garage, ample parking and a yard.  Enclosed porches add an additional 200SF of seasonal enjoyment to each 3 bedroom/1 bath unit.  Brand new roof in February 2022, vinyl replacement windows excepting enclosed porch area & Viessman Vitola 200 heating system add to the opportunity to call this yours!  
**Annual income as shown is projected for vacant 1st floor @ $1,800 Month & 3rd floor @ $1,500 Month.  2nd Floor current rent is accurate at $800.00 Month. See Income & Expense sheet.
